<br>
You can take the stance that backing out gives our country the appearance of instability but it doesn't.  When a new boss comes into the company people expect change.  Its just how it is.  Some people will lose jobs, departments will be reorganized, some people will like the new boss, and some people will miss the old boss.  <br>
<br>
Stop saying Bill Clinton lied about sex.  What a cop out.  Makes it all sound so innocent... its just sex right and people in our country lie about sex all the time.  First off we shouldn't be so comfortable with people who lie about sex or anything for that matter.  Second of all we aren't talking about a lie.  We are talking about breaking the law.  You say I don't answer questions so answer these:<br>
